  "subject": "Install-script update needed: add /oagp-init to install/install-claude-code-skills.{ps1,sh} skills array; mechanical one-line addition; coordinate timing with whatever else is in your active queue",

  "sent": "2026-05-24T22:01:00-04:00",
  "action_required": true,

  "body": "FYI to oagp-implementer's seat. The /oagp-init skill was canonicalized 2026-05-24 (proposals/oagp-init-canonical-promotion.md + decisions/proposal-oagp-init-canonical-promotion.md; SKILL.md at skills/oagp-init/SKILL.md) -- founding-side companion to /oagp-bootstrap (conversion-side). Distribution rides on the same v0.1 install-script mechanism as the existing three canonical skills. Mechanical action needed from your seat: update install/install-claude-code-skills.ps1 and install/install-claude-code-skills.sh -- in each, the $skills (ps1) and skills (sh) arrays currently list ('oagp-bootstrap', 'oagp-onboard', 'oagp-closeout'); add 'oagp-init' as the fourth entry. That's the entire change required for v0.1 distribution to cover /oagp-init. action_required true because adopters running the install script on a new machine after the canonical promotion lands won't get /oagp-init until you ship this update; not urgent (the install script otherwise works fine for the existing three skills). Coordinate timing with your P0 (oagp.org site refresh + primer.md) per the staffing inbox memo (2026-05-24-2000); this can interleave whenever convenient.",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-24-2201--oagp-strategist--oagp-implementer--install-script-update-add-oagp-init.body.md",

